msgstr "5. A Wheel Turning Monarch "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 47. Adaliddasutta → adaḷiddasuttaṃ (bj) | adaliddo (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.47:0.3"
msgid "47. Adaliddasutta "
msgstr "47. Prosperous "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: Adaliddo, adaliddo’ti → adaḷiddo adaḷiddoti (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "sn46.47:1.1"
msgid "“‘Adaliddo, adaliddo’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of someone who is ‘prosperous’. "

msgctxt "sn46.47:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, ‘adaliddo’ti vuccatī”ti? "
msgstr "How is a prosperous person defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.47:1.3"
msgid "“Sattannaṃ kho, bhikkhu, bojjhaṅgānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā ‘adaliddo’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "“Mendicant, they’re called prosperous because they’ve developed and cultivated the seven awakening factors. "

msgctxt "sn46.47:1.4"
msgid "Katamesaṃ sattannaṃ? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "sn46.47:1.5"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgassa … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgassa—"
msgstr "The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity. "

msgctxt "sn46.47:1.6"
msgid "imesaṃ kho, bhikkhu, sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā ‘adaliddo’ti vuccatī”ti. "
msgstr "They’re called prosperous because they’ve developed and cultivated these seven awakening factors.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.47:1.7"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

